I'm not sure if you're familiar
with this big grant

00:48:50.290 --> 00:48:53.590
that the business school got
at Stanford to support

00:48:53.590 --> 00:48:56.820
enterprise creation in
low income economies.

00:48:56.820 --> 00:49:02.310
But we managed to finagle a
fellow named Sara Tollefson.

00:49:02.310 --> 00:49:05.470
And she's our official
director of impact.

00:49:05.470 --> 00:49:10.000
And I felt very strongly that
impact needs to be managed by

00:49:10.000 --> 00:49:12.930
somebody who works on all
of the different teams.

00:49:12.930 --> 00:49:14.740
And Sara's got a really
