primary job requirement.

00:49:27.000 --> 00:49:28.590
So she works with Vin
and other people.

00:49:28.590 --> 00:49:32.560
And we're trying to do some
interesting things to like to

00:49:32.560 --> 00:49:34.210
get the data off the Brilliance
machines, for

